<h2 id="tips">Tips</h2>

<h3 id="start-a-new-website">Start a new website</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem <span class="nb">install </span>bundler jekyll
jekyll new new-website
<span class="nb">cd </span>new-website
bundle add webrick
bundle <span class="nb">exec </span>jekyll serve <span class="nt">--port</span> 4500 <span class="nt">--livereload</span> 
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="start-a-new-website-using-bundler">Start a new website using bundler</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">mkdir </span>bundle-init-new-site
<span class="nb">cd </span>bundle-init-new-site
bundle init
bundle config <span class="nb">set</span> <span class="nt">--local</span> path <span class="s1">'vendor/bundle'</span>
bundle add jekyll
bundle <span class="nb">exec </span>jekyll new <span class="nt">--force</span> <span class="nt">--skip-bundle</span> <span class="nb">.</span>
bundle add webrick
bundle <span class="nb">install
</span>bundle <span class="nb">exec </span>jekyll serve <span class="nt">--port</span> 4600
</code></pre></div></div>

